! --- data plane ---
interface Loopback0
 ip address 74.74.74.74 255.255.255.255
interface Ethernet0/0
 description === to RT01 ===
 ip address 10.1.12.2 255.255.255.252
 no shutdown
interface Ethernet0/1
 description === to RT03 ===
 ip address 10.1.23.1 255.255.255.252
 no shutdown
router ospf 1
 router-id 74.74.74.74
 network 74.74.74.74 0.0.0.0 area 0
 network 10.1.12.0 0.0.0.3 area 0
 network 10.1.23.0 0.0.0.3 area 0
